## Review Cycle Statuses

| Status | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| `open` | Cycle is accepting reviews. Other reviewers' submissions are hidden (prevents anchoring bias). |
| `closed` | Cycle is complete. All reviews are now publicly visible (radical transparency). |

| Outcome | Meaning |
|---------|---------|
| `advanced` | Consensus reached — node tier was advanced |
| `maintained` | Reviewers agreed the node isn't ready yet — tier unchanged, feedback visible |
| `split` | Reviewers disagreed — tier unchanged, flagged for community attention |

